8 COMMITTEE SUBSTITUTE
9 A Joint Resolution approving certain proposed
permanent major rules of the Oklahoma Health Care
10 Authority; and directing distribution.
11
12 WHEREAS, pursuant to Section 308 of Title 75 of the Oklahoma
13 Statutes, the Oklahoma State Legislature shall adopt a separate
14 joint resolution to approve or disapprove major rules.
15 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
16 AND THE SENATE OF THE 2ND SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
17 SECTION 1. The Legislature hereby approves all the following
18 proposed major rules submitted by the Oklahoma Health Care Authority
19 on or before February 1, 2026: OAC 317:30-5-47 and 317:30-5-47.7.
20 SECTION 2. The Oklahoma Secretary of State is hereby directed
21 to distribute copies of this resolution to the Governor and the
22 editor of "The Oklahoma Register".
